To set up the game a few steps need to be taken.
1. First a computer is required and terminal needs to be opened on it.
2. Then you need to create a folder and place the website file inside of that directory.
3. While you have the directory open in the terminal run the command NPM install. (this will install the react software allowing you to start the website server up.
4. Now run the command NPM start this will start the server.
5. Then copy the link to the website ( it should say localhost:: then numbers) paste it into your browser.
6. After you reach the website click on the download button which will then redirect you to the newest version of the game to download.
